how about individual project under "refs/meta/dashboards/swi-products/*" ?

Use below groups?
Cellular-Platform Legato-Admin Legato-AtSwi-Admin Mdm9xxx-Admin Mdm9x07-Admin Mdm9x28-Admin

Does this file support splitting long line into multiple lines ?

Splitting long line is a good idea. However, it does not work after after some tries.

Let's change this to below to avoid use of reviewedby:USER (does not support GROUP), although is:reviewed is applicable to any users.

NOT (label:Code-Review>=1 OR is:reviewed)

Let's change this to below to avoid use of reviewedby:USER (does not support GROUP), although is:reviewed is applicable to any users.

(label:Code-Review>=1 OR is:reviewed)

I checked the dashboard,
as Legato team has quite a lot active reviews, would you help to move it to a separate dashboard in swi-products ?

This refers to:
OR (project:manifest path:^legato.*) OR (project:ima-support-tools branch:master) OR (project:^product/.* branch:master) OR (project:^Legato/.* branch:master) OR (project:^legato-.* branch:master)

Sorry for late charges on the request.


BTW, I read the doc, it says dashboard supports inheritance. I am unsure, maybe we can use that to build a big dashboard from smaller ones.
